dm_dbo.single_result_row_view where exists (SELECT * FROM dm_folder WHERE r_object_id IN (SELECT i_folder_id FROM dm_folder WHERE r_object_id IN(SELECT i_folder_id FROM cd_submission_element WHERE r_object_id='$value(r_object_id)' and object_name not in ('index.xml','index-md5.txt'))) and object_name !='util')

dm_dbo.single_result_row_view where exists (SELECT * FROM dm_folder WHERE r_object_id IN (SELECT i_folder_id FROM dm_folder WHERE r_object_id IN(SELECT i_folder_id FROM cd_submission_element WHERE r_object_id='$value(r_object_id)' and object_name not in ('index.xml','index-md5.txt'))) and object_name !='util')
dm_dbo.single_result_row_view where exists (select * from cd_controlled_doc where wf_is_in_workflow=true and r_object_id = '$value(r_object_id)')

dm_dbo.single_result_row_view where exists (select w.r_object_id from dm_workflow w, dmi_package p where p.r_component_chron_id = '$value(i_chronicle_id)' and p.r_workflow_id = w.r_object_id and w.r_runtime_state = 1 and (w.object_name like 'Cat 1 GMP withdrawal%' or w.object_name like 'Cat 1-3 Editing Workflow%')) or exists (select r_object_id from cd_controlled_doc where r_object_id='$value(r_object_id)' and a_status = 'Effective' and can_be_withdrawn = true and planned_withdraw_date is not nulldate) enable(row_based)
